{"tid":2206002,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國首相約翰遜表示港區國安法已違反中英聯合聲明","createTime":"2020-09-17T08:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T21:56:31.000Z","uid":53844,"like":433,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"215342787138f3396982d414be2eb46b7c8eaaaf","tid":2206002,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T08:09:59.000Z","msg":"英國首相約翰遜在國會一個委員會說，北京實施港區國安法有違《中英聯合聲明》，而有關影響已經浮現，開始對港人的言論自由造成寒蟬效應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國國務卿蓬佩奧與到訪的英國外相藍韜文會面，討論香港與新疆等問題。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧說，美方歡迎英國政府最近幾個月針對中國挑戰所採取的行動，包括為港人發聲並提供庇護，藍韜文表示，英美兩國都關注香港及新疆情況，認為兩地人民的人權受到嚴重侵犯。<br />\n<br />\n他呼籲中國履行國際義務，指香港自治與人民自由受到完全尊重至關重要。<br />\n<br />\n英國會密切關注港區國安法的執行情況，及香港事態發展。"},{"pid":"2fb7e863723207d84f0bd4d9746cac5f466f8560","tid":2206002,"uid":88743,"like":213,"dislike":0,"score":213,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T08:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRjWHMF.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRjWHMF.gif&h=d30debe0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed526f052b520922499b0e1e299478074dca6515","tid":2206002,"uid":124372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T08:11:28.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"ef4c63e752f3e30178e310633813dc86e23828b0","tid":2206002,"uid":33556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T08:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490a6298cba62c8e165005203b97bd75b430de12","tid":2206002,"uid":256246,"like":29,"dislike":14,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T08:13:08.000Z","msg":"英國：一直關注🙏"},{"pid":"71b50a74c3c78ba107680a0c731c02ab8320859b","tid":2206002,"uid":127575,"like":11,"dislike":34,"score":-23,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T08:14:35.000Z","msg":"又係得把口<br />\n制裁啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cdadc793927563db6